            "critical_failure": "The cyclops seeker determines a suboptimal moment for their attack; they learn nothing useful and become off-guard until the start of their next turn.",
            "critical_success": "Until the end of their next turn, all Strikes the cyclops seeker attempts against the creature gain a +1 status bonus to the attack roll and inflict an additional 2d6 precision damage. ",
